title: Eps. 177 - Ugly Instagram
description:
Doing the work vs looking like you’re doing the work. Today’s podcast talks about the difference between the two. In today’s world of social media, it’s easier to LOOK like you’re doing the working instead of actually doing the work. In order to be successful, you have to actually do the work as well as go through a process. The guys discuss the importance of not being influenced or discouraged by what you see on social media and instead focus on the work. Obtaining real success requires REAL work in the lab and not LIKES on Instagram.
